com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.location
Interface LocationBindingRoot

public interface LocationBindingRoot

A representation of the model object 'Binding Root'.

The following features are supported:

  • Mixed
  • XMLNS Prefix Map
  • XSI Schema Location
  • Binding Entry
  • Location Binding

See Also:
